      "review_summary": "The PR adds `streaming.progress.persistProgress` plus Telegram draft-stream persistence, lossless overflow handling, CLI commentary progress plumbing, docs, generated config metadata, and focused tests.\n\nPR surface: Source +217, Tests +410, Docs +1, Generated 0. Total +628 across 21 files.\n\nReproducibility: yes. for the review finding: source inspection shows the key is added to the shared progress schema and shared formatter while the docs/proof describe Telegram behavior. I did not run validation commands because this review was read-only.",
